‚ö†Ô∏è These notes are a direct reconstruction of the lecture,
including board drawings, arrows, crossings, circles, and questions.

‚ö†Ô∏è Nothing is skipped.
‚ö†Ô∏è Repetition is intentional.
‚ö†Ô∏è Images are verbally decoded into logic and meaning.
‚ö†Ô∏è Written for GitHub + deep algorithmic understanding.

